4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity specialists, requiring no prior experience. The program spans 16 weeks, with three live online classes each week, accommodating up to 16 students per class. Key topics include Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Students will learn data loss prevention strategies and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an official completion certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop